{"tid":2076022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗：香港高官擁有外國護照不等於勾結外國勢力 中国政府本身計劃將所有案件移交至中国審理","createTime":"2020-06-23T08:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T06:13:28.000Z","uid":125168,"like":22,"dislike":276,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"4739c14c69dea9f770f356b4f947b899e4e82b5e","tid":2076022,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:34:18.000Z","msg":"譚耀宗接受《視點31》訪問講述港區国安法，重點如下：<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻中国政府會於三種情況動用管轄權處理相關案件：香港政府癱瘓、涉及外交的重大事件、中国進入戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n（補充：譚耀宗早前亦指外國人受港區国安法規管，與屬地原則吻合。）<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻中国政府本身計劃將所有案件移交至中国審理，譚耀宗認為現時方案已相當尊重一国兩制。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻譚耀宗認為香港政府高層官員毋須放棄外國護照，又指條文清晰定義「勾結」一詞。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻立法會參選人反對港區国安法或被視為不效忠基本法，因法律會納入基本法附件三。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻譚耀宗不反對行政長官指派處理案件的法官前諮詢首席法官意見。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻譚耀宗強調港人不用恐慌，形容澳門成立維護國家安全委員會後仍然馬照跑舞照跳。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/xinqisu/status/1275321358923083776?s=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fxinqisu%2Fstatus%2F1275321358923083776%3Fs%3D12&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=a3a3c205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/xinqisu/status/1275321358923083776?s=12</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港政治<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/weatherjj/26898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fweatherjj%2F26898&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=e75a09d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/weatherjj/26898</a>"},{"pid":"99414632643493f8fc5f5240d728af7544463dc5","tid":2076022,"uid":18477,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢集視點31要backup</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4