itedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:34:18.000Z","msg":"譚耀宗接受《視點31》訪問講述港區国安法，重點如下：<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻中国政府會於三種情況動用管轄權處理相關案件：香港政府癱瘓、涉及外交的重大事件、中国進入戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n（補充：譚耀宗早前亦指外國人受港區国安法規管，與屬地原則吻合。）<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻中国政府本身計劃將所有案件移交至中国審理，譚耀宗認為現時方案已相當尊重一国兩制。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻譚耀宗認為香港政府高層官員毋須放棄外國護照，又指條文清晰定義「勾結」一詞。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻立法會參選人反對港區国安法或被視為不效忠基本法，因法律會納入基本法附件三。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻譚耀宗不反對行政長官指派處理案件的法官前諮詢首席法官意見。<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻譚耀宗強調港人不用恐慌，形容澳門成立維護國家安全委員會後仍然馬照跑舞照跳。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/xinqisu/status/1275321358923083776?s=12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fxinqisu%2Fstatus%2F1275321358923083776%3Fs%3D12&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=a3a3c205\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/xinqisu/status/1275321358923083776?s=12</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港政治<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/weatherjj/26898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fweatherjj%2F26898&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JZUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=e75a09d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/weatherjj/26898</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"譚耀宗認為香港政府高層官員毋須放棄外國護照，又指條文清晰定義「勾結」一詞。<br />\n<br />\n= 譚耀宗認為效宗他國不是勾結<br />\n<br />\n<strong>UK</strong><br />\nI (name) swear by almighty God that on becoming a British citizen, <span style=\"color: red;\">I will be faithful and bear true allegiance to Her Majesty Queen Elizabeth the Second, her Heirs and Successors, according to the law. I will give my loyalty to the United Kingdom</span> and respect its rights and freedoms.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>US</strong><br />\n&quot;I hereby declare, on oath, that I absolutely and entirely renounce and abjure all allegiance and fidelity to any foreign prince, potentate, state, or sovereignty, of whom or which I have heretofore been a subject or citizen; that <span style=\"color: red;\">I will support and defend the Constitution and laws of the United States of America against all enemies, foreign and domestic; that I will bear true faith and allegiance to the same; that I will bear arms on behalf of the United States when required by the law</span>; that I will perform noncombatant service in the Armed Forces of the United States when required by the law; that I will perform work of national importance under civilian direction when required by the law; and that I take this obligation freely, without any mental reservation or purpose of evasion; so help me God.&quot;"},{"pid":"23761680e5fd81d09d3dbcfe5c223ef919625312","tid":2076022,"uid":48605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:29:40.000Z","msg":"真係要正視呢樣野"},{"pid":"4f803dd7b08fd6138ab596ec3d64b6070b1d9a09","tid":2076022,"uid":48605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:30:38.000Z","msg":"全世界係咪得香港同終國係咁？<br />\n啲高官全部外國籍"},{"pid":"bae1ac1ef1d35734f8ab3c0008693773e0ca4650","tid":2076022,"uid":129202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:30:59.000Z","msg":"香港高官擁有外國護照不等於勾結外國勢力<br />\n689不是香港高官<br />\n結論：689勾結外國勢力"},{"pid":"3c9c586ac184a9243fbd245a390449edfdf6d016","tid":2076022,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e023808bcccbaffecb2cab3af84b9f380612b729","tid":2076022,"uid":57674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"其實條文即係咁啦...<br />\n第一條「我想拉你就拉你 判你就判你 唔好問點解」<br />\n完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:33:38.000Z","msg":"咪係<br />\n<br />\n傻嘅先繼續同啲太監斟酌埋啲on9細節啫"},{"pid":"39a770487ba4a99260cc8969b9e93f6338d58d67","tid":2076022,"uid":244346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"重點：外國人受管制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ce7652729c0f1aa00ecac6929e876aab5f85f6","tid":2076022,"uid":176999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:40:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e6ca